Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:24.27,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}只是 被寫入大腦的虛象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:27.71,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}無限遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:32.21,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}不過是個 價值觀被改寫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:35.51,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}普通的平行世界
